
MAIN
1. Start 
2. Kill all FFMpeg process. Flag Recording = False
3. Get_Is_this_Time_to_record() [returns 'No' or Date_Time_Sub_Weekday string]
4. If No, sleep 5secs, go to 2
5. [assumes this is recording time and string is received]
6. If Recording = False, StartRecording()
7. If Recording = True, Get_Is_Time_to_restart_Recording() [5min sync recording to clock], 
8. Get_Is_Time_to_restart_Recording() if yes then StartRecording()
9. else, go to 3 

StartRecording()
 Create Filename with Date_Time_Sub_Weekday, 
 Start recording, 
 flag Recording as True.
